"title": "8158: righteousness, of believers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8158: righteousness, of believers",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A sincere desire to please God by keeping his law is both commanded and approved by him. However, human fallibility means that true righteousness must be the product of the Holy Spirit's work in the believer.</p>\n<h2>Righteousness includes keeping the laws of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:25\">DEU 6:25</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job27:6\">JOB 27:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:7\">1JN 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:9\">GEN 6:9</a> <em>Noah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:19\">GEN 18:19</a> <em>Abraham</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:17-Deut6:18\">DEU 6:17–6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:6\">1KI 3:6</a> <em>David</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:11\">1KI 15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:20\">2CH 31:20</a> <em>Hezekiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:8\">PSA 7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps15:1-Ps15:5\">PSA 15:1–15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:1\">PSA 17:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:11\">PSA 32:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:7\">PSA 45:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:7-Isa26:9\">ISA 26:7–26:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:18\">ISA 48:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:1\">ISA 51:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:9\">HOS 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:25\">LUK 2:25</a> <em>Simeon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:19\">ACT 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:14\">2CO 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:15-2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:15–3:16</a></p>\n<h2>God requires righteousness of his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:24\">AMO 5:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">MAT 6:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:16-Isa1:17\">ISA 1:16–1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:1\">ISA 56:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:3\">JER 22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:12\">HOS 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:3\">ZEP 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:6\">MAT 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:14\">EPH 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:11\">1TI 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:22\">2TI 2:22</a></p>\n<h2>God loves those who are righteous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:8\">PSA 146:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:9\">PRO 15:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:20\">JAS 1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:5-Ps1:6\">PSA 1:5–1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:5\">PSA 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:5\">PSA 33:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:6\">PSA 37:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:28-Ps37:30\">PSA 37:28–37:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:3\">PSA 106:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:16\">PRO 10:16</a></p>\n<h2>The righteous receive blessing from God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:28\">PRO 12:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:43\">MAT 13:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:12\">PSA 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:15\">PSA 34:15</a> <em>the LORD watches over them</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:16-Ps37:17\">PSA 37:16–37:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:22\">PSA 55:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:12\">PSA 92:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:4\">PSA 112:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:2-Prov10:3\">PRO 10:2–10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:6-Prov10:7\">PRO 10:6–10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:16\">PRO 10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:29-Prov10:32\">PRO 10:29–10:32</a> <em>they are secure</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:4-Prov11:6\">PRO 11:4–11:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:10\">ISA 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:15-Isa33:16\">ISA 33:15–33:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:3\">DAN 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16\">JAS 5:16</a> <em>their prayers are effective</em></p>\n<h2>The righteous may suffer for their faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:10\">MAT 5:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:21\">PSA 94:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:1\">ISA 57:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:6\">AMO 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:12\">AMO 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:14\">1PE 3:14</a></p>",
